    s_name,
    s_address
FROM
    'pool/supplier/*.parquet',
    'pool/nation.parquet'
WHERE
    s_suppkey IN (
        SELECT
            ps_suppkey
        FROM
            'pool/partsupp/*.parquet'

                SELECT
